{"type": "article", "id": 13652, "title": "「 夏末单车」之可以对讲的耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-18T08:03:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000250M1NcW5kSpuQGYFOw.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款运动耳机，它的特殊之处在于可以同时当作对讲机来使用，从而帮助你在运动中享受音乐的同时，如果有需要，能够轻松自如地和一起骑行的伙伴对话，而避免大声喊叫带来的尴尬和粗鲁。同时，你还可以通过它来和朋友分享音乐。另外，你可以自定义 LED 灯的颜色，让它和你出行时的装扮颜色更搭配。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/970535950/combat-sync-the-ultimate-wireless-sports-headphone\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141341aGJxlrAp3cdQ1bF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141341zes5OGlKmf0j3qJc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141342LvwdEjC5QYisg1If.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141343sIwQ1cyqzLCxh3Ao.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141343tWp0cEFduH278GmC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141344iUPue8mEGQWOzXw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.60441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141344rOP7AlJCMN3mBeHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}